ed="T" n="0810a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0810a18"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023307"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>相國寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011659">貞峻</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0810a19"/><persName key="A011659">釋貞峻</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000023249"><placeName>鄭州</placeName><placeName>新鄭</placeName></placeName>人也。<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName><persName key="A007201">張果<roleName>先生</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0810a20"/>之裔孫。今<placeName key="PL000000023066"><anchor xml:id="beg0810sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>榮</sic><corr>滎</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0810sgsz3"/>陽</placeName>有<placeName key="PL000000023154">張果里</placeName>，其墳楸檟存焉。<persName key="A011659">峻</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0810a21"/>風度寬裕，髫齡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g280"/>不弄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g928"/>。<date key="j20351992035582" from-iso="+0860-01-31" to-iso="+0861-02-17">年十四</date>，忽超然離俗，人<lb
ed="T" n="0810a22"/>莫我知。雖二親褰衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g929"/>，昆弟截路，終弗能沮<lb
ed="T" n="0810a23"/>之，乃投<placeName key="PL000000023307">相國寺</placeName><persName key="A011665">歸正<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>出家。神機駿發，<lb
ed="T" n="0810a24"/>乍觀可驚。雖背碑覆棊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g934"/>，彼不足多也。未幾，<lb
ed="T" n="0810a25"/>諷徹《淨名》、《仁王》<ptr target="#n198"/>諸經，計數萬言。時同儕戲之<lb
ed="T" n="0810a26"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A011659">汝</ref>是有脚經笥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g609"/>也。」<persName key="A011659">峻</persName>辭讓斯題，恭遜而<lb
ed="T" n="0810a27"/>已。及削染為僧形，即聽《俱舍論》<ptr target="#n1429"/>，隨講誦頌<lb
ed="T" n="0810a28"/>八品，計六百行。至<date key="j20366752037029" from-iso="+0864-02-15" to-iso="+0865-02-03">十八</date>升論座。<date key="j20373852037768" from-iso="+0866-01-25" to-iso="+0867-02-12">年滿</date>於<placeName key="PL000000023256"><placeName>嵩<lb
ed="T" n="0810a29"/>山</placeName><placeName>會善寺</placeName></placeName>戒壇院納法，因棲<placeName key="PL000000023413">封禪寺</placeName>，今號<pb ed="T" n="0810b" xml:id="T50.2061.0810b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0810b01"/><placeName key="PL000000023413">開寶律院</placeName>，學新章律疏<ptr target="#n902"/>。<date key="j20385062038860" from-iso="+0869-02-19" to-iso="+0870-02-08">二十三</date>，策名<ptr type="glossary" target="#g937"/>講授，<lb
ed="T" n="0810b02"/>長宿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g938"/><anchor xml:id="beg0810sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>積</sic><corr>稱</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0810sgsz5"/>奇。當<date from-iso="+0891-02-17" key="j20465392046892" to-iso="+0892-02-05"><name>大順</name>二年</date>，災<placeName key="PL000000023307">相國寺</placeName>，重樓三<lb
ed="T" n="0810b03"/>門，七寶佛殿，排雲寶閣、文殊殿裏廊，計四百<lb
ed="T" n="0810b04"/>餘間，都為煨燼。時<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023307">寺</ref>眾惶惶，莫知投跡。或<lb
ed="T" n="0810b05"/>曰如請得<persName key="A011659">峻</persName>歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023307">寺</ref>，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023307">寺</ref>可成矣。乃相率往<lb
ed="T" n="0810b06"/>今<placeName key="PL000000023413">開寶</placeName>，堅請<persName key="A011659">峻</persName>歸充<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023307">本寺</ref>上座。前後數年，<lb
ed="T" n="0810b07"/>重新廊廡，殿宇增華。又請為新章<ptr target="#n1550"/>宗主<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2140"/>，復<lb
ed="T" n="0810b08"/>開律講，僧尼弟子日有五十餘人，執疏聽<lb
ed="T" n="0810b09"/>采。<persName key="A011659">峻</persName>之律行，氷雪相高。<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>署</sic><corr>暑</corr></choice>無裸意，寒止<anchor xml:id="beg0810sgsz7"/>袷<anchor xml:id="end0810sgsz7"/><lb
ed="T" n="0810b10"/>衣，食惟知量<ptr type="glossary" target="#g939"/>，清約太過。<date from-iso="+0911-02-07" key="j20538332054186" to-iso="+0912-01-26"><name>乾化</name>元年</date>，臨壇秉<lb
ed="T" n="0810b11"/>法。及<placeName key="PL000000048181">梁</placeName>朝革命，所度僧尼計三千餘人。以<lb
ed="T" n="0810b12"/><date key="j20586872058687" when-iso="+0924-05-23"><name>同光</name>二年夏四月十二日</date>微疾而終。春秋七<lb
ed="T" n="0810b13"/>十八，法臘五十八。葬于寺莊，袝<persName key="A036844">慧雲<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0810b14"/>塔焉。</p>
